    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "ダンスの振り付け……参考になる本あるかしら\nやっぱり、学校の図書室より、図書館に行った方が……",
      "startTime": 6.2666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_write-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4742.607084900001,
          "startTime": 11.0092737516
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_write-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11333.333333300001,
          "startTime": 17.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "『高みを目指して』……ちょっと違うかなぁ……\n『血まみれに』……ううん、ホラーじゃないし……",
      "startTime": 17.266666476,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6756.7796389,
          "startTime": 24.0234461149
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "あら、千紗も来ていたのね\n歌詞作り中かしら。いいフレーズは浮かんだ？",
      "startTime": 27.4333331426,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、お姉ちゃん。えっと……あはは\nそれなりには順調かな？",
      "startTime": 36.9000008266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "書きたい言葉が沢山浮かんで、悩んじゃうことも\nあるんだけど。……お姉ちゃんはどんな感じ？",
      "startTime": 43.8000008266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "私も、今のところ順調よ。完成した初稿を\n{user}さんに見てもらってるところなの",
      "startTime": 53.1333318711,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "ふぇ～！？　もう初稿が完成したの？\nやっぱりお姉ちゃんは凄いなぁ",
      "startTime": 59.5200459056,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "自分のことだと、言葉にしやすいみたい\n伝えたい想いが、どんどん溢れてきたの",
      "startTime": 66.8666652044,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "実際の歌詞も、一度書き始めたらするすると浮かんで\nきて、思っていたよりスムーズに完成させられたわ",
      "startTime": 74.3666652044,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "（お姉ちゃん、もうそこまで進んでるんだ……）\n（どうしよう、私はまだ完成には程遠いや）",
      "startTime": 83.8333318711,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "（つい順調って言っちゃったけど、全然まとまってないし）\n（もし遅れたら、作曲家さんにも迷惑を掛けちゃうよね）",
      "startTime": 94.7999985378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "（……ううん。今までもこういう時に慌てちゃってたけど）\n（コツコツ頑張れば、道は開けたよね）",
      "startTime": 106.7333318711,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "（うん。だから落ち着いて……大丈夫）\n（ゆっくりでもいいから、私らしく頑張ろう……！）",
      "startTime": 115.4999985378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "千紗……？　もし行き詰まったりしたら\nいつでも相談してね？　私も手伝うから",
      "startTime": 123.7333318711,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。でも行き詰まってるってほどじゃないから\nもう少しだけ自分で頑張ってみるね",
      "startTime": 132.8999985378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "そう、分かったわ。でも……\n……ううん、なんでもない。応援してるわよ、千紗",
      "startTime": 141.9333318711,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 148.4411786238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "……千紗、どうしたのかしら？\nもう家を出る時間なのに、全然起きてこないわね……",
      "startTime": 153.5333318711,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4533.3358128000045,
          "startTime": 158.0666676839
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "わあああああああ！　が、学校に遅れちゃう！\nあっ、お、お姉ちゃん、おはよう！",
      "startTime": 161.5999985378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "こら千紗、家の中で走らないの！　もう……\nでも、寝坊なんてめずらしいわね？",
      "startTime": 169.8999893825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "あはは……寝る前に歌詞を考えてたら\nつい夜更かししちゃって……",
      "startTime": 176.7666529973,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったの……あまり夜更かししてはダメよ？\n昨日も、電車に乗り遅れそうになっていたし",
      "startTime": 184.6999863307,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "千紗にはあまり言ってこなかったことだけど\nスケジュールと体調の管理はしっかりしないと",
      "startTime": 191.7333216985,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい。最近、気が抜けちゃってたから\n明日から、ちゃんと気を付けるね",
      "startTime": 199.5333216985,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_02-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ。朝ごはん包んであるから、食べれそうな時に\n食べなさい。それと……千紗、鞄持ってないわよ？",
      "startTime": 206.8333216985,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13033.338983900023,
          "startTime": 219.8666606824
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
